questions.question: For at least 10 frames, a yellow object o0 is far from and to the right of object o1, which is itself to the right of a third object o2. Following that, for at least 5 frames, o0 is behind o1, which is shaped like a cube. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o2 is at the top left of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Color_yellow(o0), Far(o1, o0), RightOf(o1, o2)), 10); Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Shape_cube(o1)), 5); Duration((Left(o2), Top(o2)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is yellow. Subsequently, o0 is behind another object o1 and is on the left side of the frame, while o1 is to the right of a third object o2. Finally, o0 is far from o1, o1 is made of metal, and o2 is to the right of o1.
questions.dsl: Duration(Color_yellow(o0), 15); (Behind(o0, o1), Left(o0), RightOf(o1, o2)); (Far(o0, o1), Material_metal(o1), RightOf(o2, o1))

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1, which is made of rubber. Simultaneously, object o2 is yellow and is located at the top of the frame along with o1. Then, for a duration of at least 10 frames, o2 moves behind o1, and o0 is on the right side of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Color_yellow(o2), Material_rubber(o1), Top(o1), Top(o2)), 5); Duration((Behind(o2, o1), Right(o0)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1. Then, o0 is behind a third object o2, while o0 is also at the top of the frame. Finally, for a duration of at least 10 frames, o1 is at the bottom of the frame, o0 is cyan, o2 is yellow, and o1 is to the left of o0.
questions.dsl: Duration(Behind(o0, o1), 15); (Behind(o0, o2), Top(o0)); Duration((Bottom(o1), Color_cyan(o0), Color_yellow(o2), LeftOf(o1, o0)), 10)

questions.question: An object o0 is to the left of another object o1, and a third object o2 is also to the left of o1. Next, o0 moves to be both in front of and to the right of o1. Finally, for at least 15 frames, o1 is behind o0 while o2 is yellow and shaped like a sphere.
questions.dsl: (LeftOf(o0, o1), LeftOf(o2, o1)); (FrontOf(o0, o1), RightOf(o0, o1)); Duration((Behind(o1, o0), Color_yellow(o2), Shape_sphere(o2)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, an object o0 is to the left of another object o1 and o0 is also on the left side of the video frame. Following that, an object o2 is at the bottom of the frame, in front of o0, and made of metal. Lastly, o0 is yellow in color and o1 is near o2.
questions.dsl: Duration((LeftOf(o0, o1), Left(o0)), 10); (Bottom(o2), FrontOf(o2, o0), Material_metal(o2)); (Color_yellow(o0), Near(o1, o2))

questions.question: Initially, for at least 15 frames, an object o0 is far from another object o1, and a third object o2 is to the left of o1 and at the top of the frame. Subsequently, for at least 10 frames, o0 is gray and o2 is far from o1. Finally, for another duration of at least 10 frames, o2 is behind o0, and o1 is yellow.
questions.dsl: Duration((Far(o0, o1), LeftOf(o2, o1), Top(o2)), 15); Duration((Color_gray(o0), Far(o2, o1)), 10); Duration((Behind(o2, o0), Color_yellow(o1)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, there is a yellow object o0 made of metal to the right of another object o1, which is to the left of a third object o2. Object o0 is also on the right side of the video frame. Then, for another duration of at least 5 frames, o1 is behind o2. Finally, object o0 is at the top of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Color_yellow(o0), LeftOf(o1, o2), Material_metal(o1), RightOf(o0, o1), Right(o0)), 5); Duration(Behind(o1, o2), 5); Top(o0)

questions.question: Initially, a spherical object o0 is at the bottom of the video frame. Then, for at least 5 frames, o0 is yellow, is far away from another object o1, and o1 is in front of a third object o2. Finally, o2 is far away from o0, and o0 is to the right of o2.
questions.dsl: (Bottom(o0), Shape_sphere(o0)); Duration((Color_yellow(o0), Far(o1, o0), FrontOf(o1, o2)), 5); (Far(o2, o0), RightOf(o0, o2))

questions.question: An object o0 is initially in front of another object o1. Then, for at least 5 frames, o0 is yellow and on the right side of the video frame. Finally, for another duration of at least 5 frames, a green object o2 is behind o1, which is behind o0, while o0 is in front of o2.
questions.dsl: FrontOf(o0, o1); Duration((Color_yellow(o0), Right(o0)), 5); Duration((Behind(o1, o0), Behind(o2, o1), Color_green(o2), FrontOf(o0, o2)), 5)
